    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Neoaulobia cactui sp. nov. A–D—Female: A—peritremes, B, —posterior part of stylophore, C—solenidia of leg I, D—fan-like seta of tarsus IV. E–G—Male: E—peritremes, F—opisthosoma in ventral view, G—dorsal view. Scale bars: A–E = 20 µm, F–G = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2589864/files/figure.png" ;
